cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper deals with learning disentangled representations from visual data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves a deep generative model (cs.LG) that uses weak supervision (cs.AI) to learn disentangled representations. The model can also be used for tasks such as conditional image generation (cs.NE) and attribute transfer (cs.CL).
